<minor-heading id="uk.org.publicwhip/spwa/2004-10-07.S2W-10894.h" nospeaker="True" url="http://www.scottish.parliament.uk/business/pqa/wa-04/wa1007.htm#1">Asylum Seekers</minor-heading>

<ques id="uk.org.publicwhip/spwa/2004-10-07.S2W-10894.q0" speakerid="uk.org.publicwhip/member/80063" speakername="Mr Kenny MacAskill (Lothians) (SNP)" spid="S2W-10894" url="http://www.scottish.parliament.uk/business/pqa/wa-04/wa1007.htm#1">

  <p>To ask the Scottish Executive whether it is its policy to deny a child resident in Scotland looked-after status when it has been granted leave to remain in the country under asylum and immigration legislation.</p>

</ques>


